  "time_ut": 1659088283,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0d86\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9d \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Extends Western Vehicle Revenue Permit Period",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The period of non-imposition of fines for expiring vehicle licenses in the Western Province has been postponed until August 31.",
        "This is being implemented to provide relief to the public who are hindered in obtaining vehicle revenue licenses due to the existing difficulties in reaching the service stations due to the limited supply of fuel in the country.",
        "Thus, for vehicles expiring from July 29, the period of those licenses has been extended till August 31 without charging fines."
      ],
      "title_ents": [],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
